34#ifndef _DEBUGRM_H
35#define _DEBUGRM_H
36
37#define DRMDUMPFILE "/var/tmp/debugrm.dump"
38
39#ifdef NONEED_DRM
40#ifndef racoon_malloc
41#define racoon_malloc(sz) malloc((sz))
42#endif
43#ifndef racoon_calloc
44#define racoon_calloc(cnt, sz) calloc((cnt), (sz))
45#endif
46#ifndef racoon_realloc
47#define racoon_realloc(old, sz) realloc((old), (sz))
48#endif
49#ifndef racoon_free
50#define racoon_free(p) free((p))
51#endif
52#ifndef racoon_strdup
53#define racoon_strdup(p) strdup((p))
54#endif
55#else /*!NONEED_DRM*/
56#ifndef racoon_malloc
57#define racoon_malloc(sz) \
58 DRM_malloc(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (sz))
59#endif
60#ifndef racoon_calloc
61#define racoon_calloc(cnt, sz) \
62 DRM_calloc(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (cnt), (sz))
63#endif
64#ifndef racoon_realloc
65#define racoon_realloc(old, sz) \
66 DRM_realloc(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (old), (sz))
67#endif
68#ifndef racoon_free
69#define racoon_free(p) \
70 DRM_free(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (p))
71#endif
72#ifndef racoon_strdup
73#define racoon_strdup(p) \
74 DRM_strdup(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (p))
75#endif
76#endif /*NONEED_DRM*/
77
78extern void DRM_init(void);
79extern void DRM_dump(void);
80extern void *DRM_malloc(const char *, size_t, const char *, size_t);
81extern void *DRM_calloc(const char *, size_t, const char *, size_t, size_t);
82extern void *DRM_realloc(const char *, size_t, const char *, void *, size_t);
83extern void DRM_free(const char *, size_t, const char *, void *);
84extern char *DRM_strdup(const char *, size_t, const char *, const char *);
85
86#ifndef NONEED_DRM
87#define vmalloc(sz) \
88 DRM_vmalloc(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (sz))
89#define vdup(old) \
90 DRM_vdup(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (old))
91#define vrealloc(old, sz) \
92 DRM_vrealloc(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (old), (sz))
93#define vfree(p) \
94 DRM_vfree(__FILE__, __LINE__, __func__, (p))
95#endif
96
97extern void *DRM_vmalloc(const char *, size_t, const char *, size_t);
98extern void *DRM_vrealloc(const char *, size_t, const char *, void *, size_t);
99extern void DRM_vfree(const char *, size_t, const char *, void *);
100extern void *DRM_vdup(const char *, size_t, const char *, void *);
101
102#endif /* _DEBUGRM_H */
